    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Woolen garment comprising a rectangular panel, usually tucked in at the belt and wrapped in various ways around the hips and between the thighs; may be worn by males in southern South America.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
